      "birth_date": "ca. 1584 (per Wolphert Gerritsen's declaration on 4 October 1638 before the Secretary of New Netherland that he was 54 years old, NYHMD vol. 1 [Register of the Provincial Secretary, 1638-1642], pp. 65-66; cited Kouwenhoven 1997 p. 209 fn 2 = cp_sou_043). VARIANT (rejected): WikiTree '1 May 1579' traces to L.P. de Boer (1912) 'noble Coudenhove of Eindhoven' descent claim, which Kouwenhoven 1997 p. 218 establishes as specious.",
