      "children_summary": "Ten children with Saertje Frans (cp_fam_013) per Cocheu 71:1 (cp_sou_047), all bp. DRC NY:\n  67. Jacob = cp_fam_014 (existing), bp. 1664-11-30 (BDC 75); m. Newtown 1685-07-07 Anna Remerson of Gravesend (KCo 79).\n  68. Francois (died young), bp. 1666-10-10 (BDC 84). [Not minted — died young.]\n  69. Hester = cp_fam_079, bp. 1669-08-12 (BDC 95); m. NY 1688-02-22 Johannes Martier from Leyden (MDC 63).\n  70. Lysbeth = cp_fam_080, bp. 1671-03-22 (BDC 101); m. NY 1690-11-19 Abraham Mesier (MDC 69).\n  71. Jacomyntie = cp_fam_081, bp. 1673-03-25 (BDC 109); m. 1694-04-20 Wessel Pietersen (MDC 74).\n  72. Francois = cp_fam_082, bp. 1675-02-24 (BDC 118); m.(1) 1709-12-03 Catharine Olivier, m.(2) 1727-11-12 Maria Brouwn, m.(3) 1746-04-14 Hillegond Bogart widow.\n  73. Johannes = cp_fam_083, bp. 1677-04-14 (BDC 127); m. 1708-05-08 Rachel Benson.\n  74. Maria = cp_fam_084, bp. 1679-04-02 (BDC 137); m. Hendrick Brevoort 1699-04-21 (Bergen KCo 79; Riker Har 477 differs at 1699-08-26).\n  75. Catalyntie = cp_fam_085, bp. 1682-01-20 (BDC 150).\n  76. Pieter = cp_fam_086, bp. 1683-12-01 (BDC 160); m. 1707-08-09 Wyntje Ten Eyk.",
