      "spouse_text": "John Pieterse Wyckoff of NJ — son of Peter Claesen Wyckoff + Griete Van Ness; b. Flatlands 1665-02-16 (KCo 396); member Flatlands DRC 1677 (age 12); deacon 1693 (KCo 396). Will dated 1746-02-27, pro. 1746-04-25 (NJ Wills 2:553) names wife Neeltie + 7 children: Cornelius (eldest), John, Pieter, Jacob, Geertie, Neeltie, Johannes. Per Cocheu 71:2 cp_sou_048.",
