      "children_summary": "8 Mesier children (matriline; not minted as cp_fam) per Cocheu 71:3 #243-250: (243) Zara b. ~1691-08-28/29 Bergen NJ (BgnB 225), d.y.; (244) Marritje b. 1692-10-07 (BgnB 246), bp. NY 1692-11-19, m. 1711-12-26 Samuel Pell; (245) Johannes bp. NY 1696-07-29; (246) Pieter bp. NY 1698-06-19, m. NY 1721-10-07 Jannetje Wessels, bur. NY 1738-09-06; (247) Jacob (twin) bp. NY 1698-06-19; (248) Sara bp. NY 1702-04-26, m.(1) NY 1720-07-10 Vincent Tellion, m.(2) 1728-03-02 John Hendricks; (249) Annetje bp. NY 1703-12-15; (250) Elizabeth bp. NY 1708-02-18.",
      "is_enslaver": false,
