      "spouse_text": "Jan Roelofse Schenck (her cousin = #41 in Cocheu series; b. Flatlands 1670-03-01 [Schenck Gen 1911 p. 62 — note this differs from the inscription '1760' which is a typo for 1670]; d. 1753-01-30; bur. Schenck-Couwenhoven Cem cp_pla_063). Son of Roelof Martense Schenck and his 1st wife Neeltje3 Van Kouwenhoven (= cp_fam_009 — making Jan a FIRST COUSIN of Sarah). Will dated 1746-09-11, pro. 1755-06-03 (NJ Wills 3:281).",
