      "name": "Frans (Francois) Van Kouwenhoven of Greenwich",
      "name_variations": "Francois Van Couwenhoven; Francois-Fran Van Couwenhouven (rendering in genealogy.com forum discussion); Francis Cowenhoven (anglicized form); Franciscus Couwenhoven",
      "sex": "M",
      "wikitree_url": "pending — no standalone WikiTree profile located via WebSearch 2026-04-24",
      "wikitree_id": "pending follow-up (candidate for profile creation)",
      "birth_date": "before 1675-02-24 (baptism)",
