      "children_summary": "4 Williamsen children per Cocheu 71:3 #193-196 (matriline; not minted as cp_fam): (193) Elbert of Freehold NJ bp. Mar 1724 FM, m. 1752-12-06 Willemtje Schenck (NJMar 439); (194) Aert bp. 1727-01-01 FM; (195) David m. 1745-12-05 Fammetje Swarts; (196) Jannetje bp. 1732-08-03 FM.",
      "is_enslaver": false,
