      "spouse_text": "Joris Jeronimus Rapelje of Bedford (eldest son of Jeronimus Rapelje + Ann Denise); b. Wallabout 1668-11-05 (Riker Mss., NYPL); d. Cripplebush LI 1697; inv. of estate 1697-10-16. m. Brooklyn 1695-07-27 (Bklyn 143). Cocheu inserts caveat: 'At least four generally accepted authorities give marriage as of 1694 and death of husband as of 1697, recording the birth of four children during that period. Any proof to correct will be welcome.'",
      "children_summary": "4 Rapelje children (matriline; not minted as cp_fam) per Cocheu 71:3 #222-225: (222) Annetje bp. Brooklyn 1696-10-18, m. Johannes Lott (KCo 191); (223) Jacob settled Raritan NJ, m. Sarah Brinckerhoff (AnN 293); (224) Cornelius of NY, m. Johanna Antonides dau. of Vincentius Antonides (KCo 234); (225) Jeronimus of Wallabout, d. 1762-02-08, m. Hilletje Van Vechten dau. of Hendrick Claesen Van Vechten (KCo 364), d. 1775-07-10 ae. 91.",
