      "father_text": "Jacob Willemse van Couwenhoven (cp_ens_009) — HYPOTHESIS based on (a) \"Roeloff\" named as executor in Jacob's 1743 will; (b) administrator Peter Covenhoven likely brother (Jacob's son Peter); (c) Hendrickson kin-network in probate matches Jacob's daughter Annetje married Hendrickson",
