      "spouse_text": "Jannetje Hendrickson — m. 1741-08-12 Freehold-Middletown Dutch Reformed Church (Cocheu 82:2 #161 [cp_sou_055]). After Roelof's death, Jannetje m.(2) 1747 Peter Schenck (cousin, son of cp_fam_071 + Jan Roelofse Schenck = #145), and had 6 Schenck children (per Cocheu 82:2). Widow declined administration 1746-12-20.",
      "children_summary": "3 children (per Cocheu 82:2 #161 [cp_sou_055]): (1) Sarah⁶ bap. 1742-02-21 FM, m. 1763-07-11 Benjamin Van Cleef b. 1742-09-19 (son of Benjamin Van Cleef + Elinor Covenhoven cp_fam_115/#441); (2) Daniel⁶ bap. 1744-01-15, d. 1821-02-18 probably unmarried; (3) Catrina⁶ bap. 1746-02-16, d. 1811-11-21, m. 1765-02-28 David Vanderveer b. 1748-08-02 d. 1810 (son of Teunis + Aeltje Gerretse Schenck Vanderveer) — 6 children including Roelof (m. Nelly Lloyd, daughter of Sarah Covenhoven #508).",
      "is_enslaver": true,
