      "children_summary": "Per 1781 will: Son Johannes Couwenhoven (alive 1781); Son Necasie Couwenhoven (dec'd by 1781, leaving widow Nieltie + 6 children: granddaughters Antie, Geertie, Sarah, Elizabeth, Nieltie + grandson Garret); Daughter Sarah Couwenhoven (m. Martin Schenck). Additional children possibly via 1st wife Sarah; pending FAMILY-sheet expansion in separate chat.",
