      "children_summary": "6 children per Cocheu 83:2 #677-682 (cp_sou_061); will mentions Jacob, Garret, Peter, Rachel: (677) Jacob⁶ bap. 1768-10-30 Schraalenburg, d. 1848-11-04 Leonia NJ, m. 1796-05-17 Aletta Westervelt — Jacob Cowenhoven of Liberty Pole / Englewood NJ (commonly confused with cp_ens_064 Jacobus⁷ of Westchester); (678) Hendrick; (other children TBD via Cocheu 83:2 pull). [Full list to enrich from Cocheu 83:2 in subsequent commit.]",
