      "notable_records": "Cocheu NYG&BR 71:4 #264 (cp_sou_050) — primary genealogical attestation; Cocheu 83:2 #677-682 (cp_sou_061) — children list and Berdan spouse confirmation; 1781-11-20 Will (NJA:35:238) — proved 1783-06-27; 1783-09-22 — posthumous identification as former enslaver in Black Loyalist Directory Book 2 p. 151 by Jack (cp_per_232), who registered for evacuation to Annapolis Royal aboard ship LORD TOWNSHEND (cp_eve_166, cp_sou_078).",
