      "children_summary": "[2026-05-10 per Cocheu 82:2 #522 / cp_sou_055] Eldest son **Jacob⁶ (= cp_ens_032 \"Jacob the miller of Freehold\")** bap. 1752-01-19 FM, d. 1815-04-28; three wives; 15 children including cp_ens_033 Rulef Conover. Other children #523-#529: Antje d.y., Saartje (m. Joris Smock 1779), Arie (bap. 1760), Catharina (m. Hendrick Lane 1782, removed to Carlisle Warren Co. OH), Nelly (twin to Catharina, m. Joris Lane in double wedding), Antje⁶ bap. 1773-09-05, John (mentioned in uncle Jacob Van Doren's will).",
