      "notes": "PID consolidation 2026-05-10: cp_fam_134 (later mint 2026-05-09) absorbed into cp_ens_036 (older PID 2026-04-30) per single-sheet + older-PID rule. Pre-consolidation cp_fam_134 row content preserved. Identity now MATCH: Matthias (Martin) born 1725-03-04, died 1765-10-22 age 40y 7m 18d, m. cousin Williampe Covenhoven 1749, 8 children, will dated 1765-10-08 / proved 1766-04-23 with £1,254:5:0 inventory (largest of Jacob Willemse line). Cousin marriage to Williampe Covenhoven daughter of cp_fam_101 (Cornelis-line × Jacob-line cross). Original 2026-04-30 mint as RESEARCH-TARGET (\"Martin Covenhoven\") now resolved.",
