      "children_summary": "## 83:3 enrichment (cp_sou_058):\n1 known child: Isaiah⁶ b.-; m. Elizabeth —. They had a son William⁷ b. abt. 1800 in Port Republic, NJ, who m. Rebecca, dau. of John Conover (cp_fam_???). Isaiah⁶ may be the one who m. Elizabeth Franklin 1797-02-26 in Gloucester Co. (Glou. Co. Mar.D:24, by Richard Higbee) but unverified.",
