      "notes": "Cocheu NYG&BR 71:4 (cp_sou_050) — child of cp_fam_088 John #88 of Great Egg Harbor NJ.\n\n## SOURCE-NAME ENRICHMENT (cp_sou_058 — Cocheu NYG&BR 83:3 #290)\nCocheu 83:3 (cp_sou_058) #290 — full will + 4 children:\n\n## Will + estate\n- Of Galloway Township, Gloucester Co. when he made his will.\n- Will dated 1779-04-01 / proved 1779-05-21 (NJA:34:113).\n- Wife: Sarah —.\n- Executors: wife Sarah + Joseph Estell.\n- Witnesses: David Conover (likely cp_fam_089's son David⁵), Sarah Dole (likely his sister cp_fam_184's daughter), Japhet Leeds.\n\n## 4 children (NOT yet minted as cp_fam — Tier 3 deferred):\n(a) Sarah⁶ b.-.\n(b) Mary⁶ b.-.\n(c) Elias⁶ b. ~1770; d. 1854-06-01 Tanners Brook NJ aged 84. m. before 1798 Polly Newberry b. ~1775 d. 1857-02-18 Tanners Brook aged 82.\n(d) Joseph⁶ b.-; no further record.\n\n## Distinguishing this Peter⁵ from his cousin #282\n- Same Galloway Township residence. Different wife (Sarah vs Katherine). Different will date (1779 vs 1777). Children's names overlap (both have Sarah, Mary) but #290's distinctive son is Elias⁶ (Tanners Brook).",
