      "children_summary": "Per 1812 will abstract: Robert Covenhoven (son, co-executor, recipient of cp_per_088 David); William T. Covenhoven (a.k.a. William I., son, co-executor, received 10 ac. pine land); John I. Covenhoven b.1784- (son, received home plantation, $393.95½ inventory charge; FindAGrave Family Members); Elizabeth Robinson née Covenhoven (daughter, Applegate lot + $2,500); Leah Covenhoven Ten Eyck b.1787-d.1832 (daughter, $2,500; FindAGrave Family Members)",
      "is_enslaver": true,
