      "children_summary": "George Cowenhoven (cp_ens_018, b.1764-06-09, d.1805-04-13 aged 40); John Nicholas \"John N.\" Cowenhoven (cp_ens_019, 1769-1806, documented inheritor of New Utrecht properties at father's 1793 death — planned ENSLAVER row Stage C-3); other children pending Chris's primary research.",
