      "notable_records": "(1) GRAVESTONE — New Utrecht Cemetery, Bensonhurst, Kings Co. NY: 'wife of Nicholas Cowenhoven, Esq., ae 72 yrs 5 mos 12 dys'. Find a Grave Memorial #66234784 (https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/66234784/jane-cowenhoven) — 3 gravestone photographs by Christopher Barnes (Chris). (2) TOWN OF NEW UTRECHT BIRTHS AND MANUMISSIONS — 1816 birth indenture for Peter cp_per_024 under 1799 NY gradual emancipation law; Jane recorded as enslaver age 71, three years before her death.",
