      "notes": "Cocheu 81:4 (cp_sou_053) #381 — son of #121 William cp_fam_101 + 2nd wife Antje Hendrickson (his half-brother #380 Williampe was by 1st wife Jannetje Wyckoff).\n\n## Will\nNJA:40:81 — 1806-09-26, probated 1806-10-21. Names daughters Lydia Covenhoven + Anne + Nelly Van Horne; sons-in-law Abraham + Cornelius Van Horne; sister Catherine Van Brunt + her 2 children Daniel + Sally Van Brunt; granddaughter Caty Polhemus. Executors: Cornelius Van Horne (Somerset Co., friend) + Rev. Abraham Van Horne of Caughnewaga [Fonda] NY. Witnesses: Tobias Polhemus + Timothy Murphy + Eleanor Brewer.\n\n## 6 children (per Cocheu)\n- Anne bp 1767-12-06 m. Abraham Van Horne\n- Nelly bp 1771-02-24 m. Cornelius Van Horne\n- John b 1772-05-24 d 1788-04-04 (gravestone)\n- Christopher b 1774-02-19 d 1775-03-16 (gravestone)\n- Lydia bp 1778-12-20 m. Daniel Polhemus\n- William Hendrick b 1782-03-14 d 1805-09-26 unmar ae 23-6-12 (EDSM:138 + Ap.iii) || Cocheu citation (moved from full_name 2026-05-13): Cocheu #381",
