      "name_variations": "Cornelius C. Conover (anglicized form, used on inventory title page); Cornelius C. Covenhoven (Dutch form, used on inventory affidavit + cp_per_176 1813 transaction); the 'C.' middle initial = Cornelius-son patronymic per Monmouth Dutch convention (parallel to 'R.' Rem-son in cp_ens_005/008, 'N.' Nicholas-son, 'I.' Johannes/John-son)",
