      "name_variations": "Ruliff Kovenhoven (Active R196 col Z 1809 manumission); Ruliff Covenhoven (Active R196 col M); Ralph Kovenhoven (nickname per FaG gravestone + FS profile); R.K. (gravestone initials, Milton Cem PA)",
