      "father_text": "Nicasius (Nicholas) Cowenhoven (per Chris 2026-04-25); confirmed by cp_fam_033 Gerret's 1781 will naming 'deceased son Necasie' with widow Nieltie + grandson Garret. Nicasius died bef. 1781. Likely a future cp_fam_054 candidate.",
