      "notable_records": "1815-01-16 BBB retroactive filings covering: cp_eve_039 (births of Sarah cp_per_213 + Sarah cp_per_214) backdated to 1808-03-25 + cp_eve_059 (birth of Hannah cp_per_215) backdated to 1811-06-15. Both certificates on single BBB page (MonmouthSlaveBirths_p050.pdf), filed same day as neighbor cp_ens_046 Col Elias Conover's cp_eve_063 (Maria + Susan 1814-07-07). Late-filing pattern (1815 covering 1808+1811 births) is unusual; trigger unidentified but does not weaken attribution.",
