      "occupation": "Farmer (Flatlands family farm, presumed inheritance/co-tenancy from father cp_ens_026); **Town Clerk of Flatlands 1815-1817** (succeeded father in office; succession pattern documented in feedback_flatlands_town_clerk_succession.md). Father was Town Clerk to 1815, son served 1815-1817 — possibly inheriting/passing the office on to a successor we haven't yet identified for post-1817.",
      "father_text": "William Kouwenhoven (cp_ens_026)",
