      "notes": "Child (i) of Cocheu 82:4 #659 Johannes⁶ (= cp_ens_013) by his 3rd wife Catharine Stellenwerf (= cp_ens_017). One of 10 children of Johannes⁶ across 3 marriages per Cocheu; one of 4 by Catharine. Lived adult life in New Utrecht; died at age 31 with no children. The 'Capt.' rank in the obit is the only military datum about him — Cocheu omits it. Identification of obit ↔ Cocheu ↔ cp_fam_300 cross-confirmed by exact death date match (1826-07-22), age fit (\"in the 32d year\" = 31, matches b. 1795-01-11), and New Utrecht residence.",
