      "children_summary": "Includes son Garret (named per Dutch convention after uncle Garret Rezo Covenhoven cp_ens_041). Mary Vanderveer survived Daniel D. by decades — EDSM bio c.1915: 'His widow...is still living on the homestead with their son, Garret. She is remarkably active and hale for one so near the century mark.'",
